Ideas to implement

- Add season resets with seasonal leaderboard history.
- Show recent match history on each account page.
- Add profile badges for milestones like 100 wins or 1000 correct words.
- Track longest correct streak and fastest average WPM.
- Add a "friends" or "favorite players" list.
- Let players spectate public and private lobbies.
- Add rematch voting for private lobbies.
- Add lobby host controls for private rooms.
- Add difficulty voting before a new private match starts.
- Show a short round recap after each elimination game.
- Add anti-spam cooldowns or mute tools for lobby chat.
- Add an option to disable chat entirely in a lobby.
- Add a profanity filter for usernames and chat.
- Add sound settings like master volume and mute music/audio cues.
- Add alternate voices or pronunciations for words.
- Add a practice mode with no stat changes.
- Add a daily challenge with one shared leaderboard.
- Add custom word sets for private lobbies.
- Add an "incorrect words review" page for each account.
- Add account avatars or profile themes.
- Add replay/share links for strong performances.
- Add achievements and progression levels.
- Add a queue or matchmaking mode instead of manual public joining.
- Add reconnection support if someone refreshes mid-game.
- Add admin tools to edit bad stats or remove fake accounts.
- Add automated tests for account stats, lobby limits, and WPM tracking.
